，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y20Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=19ed8fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"}]}